    category: 'action',
    helpText: 'Active participation in league governance is crucial for ensuring your team meets all competitive requirements and has input on rules that affect your season. Contact league administrators to schedule mandatory meetings covering registration deadlines, rule changes, tournament brackets, and referee assignments. This direct involvement helps you stay informed about important decisions, build relationships with other team representatives, and ensure your team complies with all league standards while advocating for your team\'s interests.'
  },
  {
    id: 'prompt-40',
    prompt: 'Research and book practice fields or court time for the entire season with backup options confirmed',
    category: 'action',
    helpText: 'Securing consistent practice facilities is fundamental to maintaining regular training schedules and team development throughout your season. Contact local parks, community centers, and sports complexes to reserve weekly time slots that work for your team\'s schedule, and arrange backup venues for weather-related cancellations or scheduling conflicts. This proactive booking ensures your team never misses valuable practice time due to facility unavailability and demonstrates professional planning to players and parents.'
  }
];</parameter>
